name: Goose Duck Goose
description:
Goose Duck Goose is an infinite runner where you play as a goose dodging obstacles and collecting your precious bread along the way.

Earn powerups with the bread you collect to try and beat your highscore!

Credits

  • All code and UI by Cam
  • All artwork and modelling by Natalia
  • Audio by Looperman (www.looperman.com)
